name: Tish James
tweet: New York has some of the country’s toughest gun laws, but too many guns are illegally trafficked from other states and our communities pay the price.   From gun trafficking takedowns to buybacks we will continue to use the power of this office to save lives.  https://t.co/8YMEifsjgX

name: Tish James
tweet: People often ask me, “Why do you call yourself the People’s Lawyer?”   My answer? Because my job is to protect the people of New York, and ensure their needs are met at every level. I serve the people of New York by any means necessary.

name: Tish James
tweet: Let’s agree to make history, to break ground, and build a more fair society as we recover from this pandemic.  There is no upstate or downstate way to make government work, but we must ensure better outcomes for the people of NY. The status quo won’t do.

name: Tish James
tweet: When we adopt inclusive policies that honor every individual’s rights with dignity, we create a fairer, more just, and more prosperous society for today and tomorrow’s New Yorkers.

name: Tish James
tweet: Today, I met with leaders on Long Island to discuss how we can preserve affordable housing. I have fought tirelessly to keep New Yorkers in their homes. name: Tish James
tweet: Every individual deserves to work where they are valued, but too often workers endure unlawful advances that put their lives and livelihood at risk.  Under my office, sexual harassment will never be tolerated. We will continue to fight for brave women who share their stories.

name: Tish James
tweet: Today marks one year since the horrific anti-Asian hate crime that left 8 dead in Atlanta. As we remember those lost in this tragic shooting, and those lost to the rise in anti-Asian violence, I vow to work to build a New York where everyone feels safe regardless of race.

name: Tish James
tweet: New York, we are in the midst of our recovery. What are you excited to see improved as we build back?
